Date: Wed, 3 Aug 2005 09:12:37 -0700 (PDT)
From: Linus Torvalds <>
Subject: Re: [patch 2.6.13-rc4] fix get_user_pages bug
Sender: linux-kernel-owner@vger.kernel.org
Precedence: bulk
List-ID: <linux-kernel.vger.kernel.org>
